<section class="section is-medium">
  <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">商业挑战</h2>
            <div class="columns">
                <div class="column card uc">
                    <div class="card-content bc">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">许多利益相关者</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">目前，多个不同的政府机构参与了此重复过程，并使用非结构化数据。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

