                    <div class="card-content bc">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">现有系统</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">我们在组织中的这些流程上使用量身定制的IT系统，而替换它们将是沉重的负担，并伴有相关成本。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</section>


<section class="section is-medium secondary">
  <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">解决方案概述</h2>
            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">关于流程</h3>
                    <p class="muted">这些过程非常繁琐，即使使用传统的传真机，也提供了许多非结构化数据。 LTO的分布式业务逻辑允许所有政府机构信任数据的有效性。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:130px;position:relative;" data-src="/assets/icons/diagram-purple.svg" alt="LTO Network - The Process">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                   <img class="lazy" style="width:130px;position:relative;" data-src="/assets/icons/link-purple.svg" alt="LTO Network - Data sharing">
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">资料共享</h3>
                    <p class="muted">通过LTO的分布式数据处理，可以通过在利益相关者办公室运行的链接（旧版）系统交换数据。 因此，区块链的实现不应要求替换其他可以正常工作的系统。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">公民的参与</h3>
                    <p class="muted">根据工作流程的状态，市民（受害者，犯罪者）可以通过其（移动）DigiD应用程序接收有关流程的过滤信息，从而无需与地区检察官办公室电话联系了解状态更新。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:130px;position:relative;" data-src="/assets/icons/desktop-purple.svg" alt="LTO Network - Citizen engagement">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <a href="/cn/contact/" class="button is-primary">预约样版</a>
            </div>
        </div>
</section>

